          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".Two computer codes ALICE-IPPE and IMPIRE."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TTY-C"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".From the measured excitation functions of the",
                "nuclear reactions Tb-165(p,n) and La-139(p,n), the",
                "yield of Dy-159 and Ce-139 radionuclides were",
                "calculated.The optimum energy range for the production",
                "of Dy-159 is E(p)-max=14 E(p)-min=6 MeV with a value",
                "of 0.9 MBq/muAhr and for the production of Ce-139 is",
                "E(p)-max=14.3 E(p)-min=8 MeV with a value of",
                " 8.57 MBq/muAhr integral yield."
              ]
            }
          ],
